{"tid":711270,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"要換全屋分體式冷氣機求教","createTime":"2018-06-21T11:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T13:37:24.000Z","uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"109f55c5fc0631496017b2fdc384b0c701bb1aee","tid":711270,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"屋企冷氣都十年有多，近排廳個部唔涼，整就一定要搭棚（我屋苑設計戇尻），所以應該都唔整，兩房一廳一炮過換晒，兩部一匹，一部兩匹。<br />\n<br />\n而家煩緊搵咩師父，好同唔好既師父真係差好遠，我唔介意比貴少少，但唔識工程野，啲師父都亂裝我都唔知，有無連登仔比下意見？<br />\n<br />\n聽人講裝唔好又會漏水又唔凍，到時又比多啲錢又要煩就慘。又話搭個棚手勢唔好會外牆漏水.......搞到我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n牌子就打算用日立，雖然大金名牌，但屋企人三年前換左部日立冷暖窗口分體，幾靜幾涼，印象幾好<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔點睇？"},{"pid":"d2c1e712e2d7f277dc3a745479895ab8b5d728c3","tid":711270,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b538c30b34049fe427bd50a6bafc2d050377f6","tid":711270,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"近排我間房換咗部大金 R32 分體，1匹 好撚凍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漏水呢啲係裝工問題，正常裝工會有保養<br />\nbtw 聽巴打講大金泰國機好似靚過馬拉機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fbef8a5e8b19ca0fe4305513b5e53a6009c3a1","tid":711270,"uid":154533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"理論上大金最好啦"},{"pid":"dd7b70719cd38f0e250acd42474cefdf8f2c8173","tid":711270,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b538c30b34049fe427bd50a6bafc2d050377f6","tid":711270,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTi